		<section id="ANM-S4J-NDB">
			<title>Hyphenation</title>
			<table rowsep="1" colsep="1" id="llx_cl1_rx">
				<tgroup cols="2">
					<colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1.0*"/>
					<colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="5cm"/>
					<thead>
						<row id="BZ5-T4J-NDB">
							<entry>Rule to check (minimal 5 characters)</entry>
							<entry>Test-Text</entry>
						</row>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
						<row id="CZ5-T4J-NDB">
							<entry>After a dot, underscore or @, wenn ein letter of a digit follows</entry>
							<entry><codeph>VERY_LONG_IDENTIFIER_WITH_UNDERSCORE VERY_LONG_IDENTIFIER_WITH_UNDERSCORE VERY_LONG_IDENTIFIER_WITH_UNDERSCORE</codeph><codeph>
								VERY.LONG.IDENTIFIER.WITH.DOTS VERY.LONG.IDENTIFIER.WITH.DOTS VERY.LONG.IDENTIFIER.WITH.DOTS</codeph><codeph>VERY@LONG@IDENTIFIER@WITH@ATS VERY@LONG@IDENTIFIER@WITH@ATS
								VERY@LONG@IDENTIFIER@WITH@ATS</codeph></entry>
						</row>
						<row id="DZ5-T4J-NDB">
							<entry>After at least two lower case letters when a captial letter follows</entry>
							<entry><codeph>VeryLongIdentifierWithCamelCase VeryLongIdentifierWithCamelCase VeryLongIdentifierWithCamelCase VeryLongIdentifierWithCamelCase</codeph> <codeph>shRt shRt
								shRt shRt shRt shRt shRt shRt shRt</codeph></entry>
						</row>
						<row id="EZ5-T4J-NDB">
							<entry>After at least wto letters when at least two digits are following</entry>
							<entry><codeph>Testcase123 Testcase123 Testcase123 Testcase123 Testcase123 Testcase123</codeph> <codeph>Testcase1 Testcase1 Testcase1 Testcase1 Testcase1
								Testcase1</codeph></entry>
						</row>
						<row id="FZ5-T4J-NDB">
							<entry>After at least two digits when at least two letters are following</entry>
							<entry><codeph>123Testcase 123Testcase 123Testcase 123Testcase 123Testcase 123Testcase </codeph> <codeph>1Testcase 1Testcase 1Testcase 1Testcase 1Testcase 1Testcase
								1Testcase</codeph></entry>
						</row>
					</tbody>
